origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "Insurance.service_comparison",
        "description": "比较不同保险服务的优劣，帮助用户选择最适合的保险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison",
                "description": "返回不同保险服务的比较结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.tax_optimization_strategy",
        "description": "提供税务优化策略，帮助用户在购买保险时最大化税务优惠。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "description",
                "description": "返回税务优化策略的详细描述。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.case_study",
        "description": "提供保险案例研究，帮助用户了解不同保险产品的实际应用和效果。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "case_study",
                "description": "返回保险案例研究的详细内容。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.recommendation",
        "description": "根据用户的需求和风险偏好，推荐最适合的保险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "recommendation",
                "description": "返回推荐的保险产品列表。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.premium_calculator",
        "description": "根据用户输入的保险需求和条件，计算保险费用。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "coverage_amount",
                "description": "保险覆盖金额。"
            },
            {
                "name": "term",
                "description": "保险期限。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "additional_coverage",
                "description": "附加保险选项。"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "premium",
                "description": "返回计算出的保险费用。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.claim_processing_status",
        "description": "查询保险理赔的处理状态。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "claim_id",
                "description": "理赔申请的唯一标识符。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "status",
                "description": "返回理赔申请的当前处理状态。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.policy_renewal_reminder",
        "description": "提醒用户保险政策的续保日期。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "policy_id",
                "description": "保险政策的唯一标识符。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "renewal_date",
                "description": "返回保险政策的续保日期。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
